Within the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]], "'''Sitrep'''" (short for 'situation report') was the request for an immediate appraisal of the current situation as faced by the unit from which the report was requested. This term was mainly used by the Republic [[Clone commando/Legends|commandos]], however other military forces likely used it as well.

